{"title":"[搜索算法]组合的输出","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":256,"tags":[],"operation":{"submit":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/problem/131#submit_code","submissions":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/submissions?problem_id=131","statistics":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/problem/131/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/problem/131/testdata","discussion":"https://oj.iqzsy.xyz/discussion/problem/131"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"排列与组合是常用的数学方法，其中组合就是从n个元素中抽出r个元素（不分顺序且r<=n），我们可以简单地将n个元素理解位自然数1，2，…，n，从中任取r个数。\r\n现要求你用递归的方法输出所有组合。\r\n例如 n=5，r=3，所有组合为：\r\n1 2 3    1 2 4    1 2 5    1 3 4    1 3 5    1 4 5    2 3 4    2 3 5    2 4 5    3 4 5\r\n\r\n"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"一行两个自然数n、r(1<n<21,1<=r<=n)。"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"所有的组合，每一个组合占一行且其中的元素按由小到大的顺序排列，每个元素占三个字符的位置，所有的组合也按字典顺序。\r\n"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"样例输入\r\n```\r\n5 3\r\n```\r\n样例输出\r\n```\r\n  1  2  3\r\n  1  2  4\r\n  1  2  5\r\n  1  3  4\r\n  1  3  5\r\n  1  4  5\r\n  2  3  4\r\n  2  3  5\r\n  2  4  5\r\n  3  4  5\r\n```\r\n"}]}